-.25in;mso-hyphenate:none;tab-stops:.25in .5in .75in"><span style="font-size:
10.0pt;letter-spacing:-.1pt"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </span>
        &nbsp;WE BELIEVE that the Holy Spirit was poured out on the Church at Pentecost in 
power,101 baptizing believers into the Body of Christ102 and releasing the gifts of the Spirit 
to them.103 The Spirit brings the permanent indwelling presence of God to us104 for 
spiritual worship,105 personal sanctification,106 building up the Church,107 gifting us for 
ministry,108 and driving back the kingdom of Satan by the evangelization of the world109 
through proclaiming the word of Jesus110 and doing the works of Jesus.111 
