        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;mso-hyphenate:
none;tab-stops:.25in"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;letter-spacing:-.1pt">WE BELIEVE that the Holy Spirit indwells every believer in Jesus Christ112 and that He is 
our abiding Helper,113 Teacher,114 and Guide.115 We believe in the filling or the 
empowering of the Holy Spirit,116 often a conscious experience,117 for ministry today.118 
We believe in the present ministry of the Spirit119 and in the exercise of all of the biblical 
gifts of the Spirit.120 We practice the laying on of hands for the empowering of the 
Spirit,121 for healing,122 and for recognition and empowering of those whom God has 
ordained to lead and serve the Church.123
